{"tid":2071211,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 一人一個對抗臭狐同事方法","createTime":"2020-06-19T15:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T13:31:16.000Z","uid":231980,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aaa685dfcfa8337bc1a323f406172f56c6d10fd3","tid":2071211,"uid":231980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T15:44:21.000Z","msg":"有位同事極量級臭狐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個重利害法係成個office 都聞到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢入職已經偷偷地送咗支日本去體味嘅藥用止汗劑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但而家夏天一到 屌仲勁左<br />\n<br />\n想當日佢除開件羽絨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心曠神怡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />提神醒腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日佢乜都唔做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />陣味已經繞梁三日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />齒頰留香 <br />\n<br />\n我依家坐喺隔離 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真心想死<br />\n<br />\n中午食完個飯返嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我有反胃嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n一人一個 可以除氣味或者暗示到佢注意下呢個問題"},{"pid":"e9dea4d9af6783e67a9fd3ff1257b9567852d893","tid":2071211,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T16:06:53.000Z","msg":"你臭過佢就得"},{"pid":"119911d03196bdcbcd7c592283a2bf087cd3aec1","tid":2071211,"uid":31738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T16:08:37.000Z","msg":"之前同事都有呢個問題<br />\n個阿姐係隔離位噴香水、空氣清新劑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑到我"},{"pid":"1eb8d7c28f4deceeea9f3e715dff8cb0cea06c6f","tid":2071211,"uid":231980,"like":0,"disli